OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782125278
OL,3,CPeston: Does Labour need a leadership
OL,4,Ccontest if Burnham is expected to win
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FTheir working assumption is that he
OL,8,Fwill exit Number 10 sometime around
OL,9,Fthe Labour conference in late
OL,10,FSeptember, though no one knows for
OL,11,Fsure.
OL,13,FThat said, the question of whether or
OL,14,Fnot there will be a proper leadership
OL,15,Fcontest will be open for a few days.
OL,17,FThe settled position of Labour MPs and
OL,18,Fmembers is that Andy Burnham is likely
OL,19,Fto be the UK's next prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
