CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782125278
OL,3,CPeston: Does Labour need a leadership
OL,4,Ccontest if Burnham is expected to win
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FBut that is absolutely not the same
OL,8,Fthing as saying they are
OL,9,Foverwhelmingly against a contest.
OL,11,FWhat they are considering is the risk
OL,12,Fof appointing Burnham by acclamation
OL,13,Fwithout subjecting him to proper
OL,14,Fscrutiny in a leadership contest,
OL,15,Fversus the risk that such a contest
OL,16,Fwill undermine "functional" government
OL,17,Ffor weeks and paint their government
OL,18,Fas no less chaotic than the previous
OL,19,FTory government.
OL,26,@xD@POUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
