PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782125278
OL,3,CPeston: Does Labour need a leadership
OL,4,Ccontest if Burnham is expected to win
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FTo put it another way, can MPs
OL,8,Fgenuinely trust that Burnham has a
OL,9,Fcredible plan for economic renewal if
OL,10,Fhe is left to formulate it in semi-
OL,11,Fprivacy? And what kind of image about
OL,12,Ftoday's Labour Party is projected if
OL,13,Fthe party simply appoints another
OL,14,Fwhite middle-aged man as leader
OL,15,Fwithout any kind of challenge?
OL,17,FThe uncertainty brought by a contest
OL,18,Fversus the perception of arrogance and
OL,19,Fmonoculture that would be the result
OL,20,Fof a Burnham coronation? It is by no
OL,21,Fmeans an easy decision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
